      NOTE: These UI packs are automatically shared for all team members with valid license.

      BYOC is Build Your Own Component

      Bridge designer-developer workflow by bringing code based components into wireframe design. BYOC helps to write custom components with HTML and CSS and incorporate it as part of your UI design. It also provides first-class support of Tailwind framework. Learn more

      Build Your Own Component using AI

      10/10 credits available for today
      Few suggestions for you to get started
      • A horizontal navigation bar with four links
      • A button with text Getting Started styled with purple gradient as background
      • A bulletin list of 5 food recipes styled with good spacing and grey color scheme
      • A table with 3 columns and 5 rows containing sample data
      • A card container with a sample placeholdit image styled like bootstrap ui
